reviewText: Its ok program... Its old from like the late 1980s but it can give you some ideas the video quality was fair condition.

great video for the proper layout and execution of building a deck. The manufacturer Taunton press no longer makes this DVD, why I don't know. If you can find it on amazon used you should definitely get it.

I am pretty sure anyone at any level will get a lot out of this DVD.  I started as a complete novice and was able to completely replace the deck of my house.  It took a while but the DVD gave some key ideas that really saved me a whole lot of time.

This was a good video all in all...
Good for learning basic decking skills.
